entry.title: JIMI: ALL IS BY MY SIDE Official Trailer

media:group.media:description:
Available In Theaters: September 26, 2014
OutKast's AndrÃ© Benjamin stars as Jimi Hendrix in this revealing biopic from Academy Award-winning writer-director John Ridley (12 Years A Slave). Covering a year in Hendrix's life from 1966-67 as an unknown backup guitarist playing New York's Cheetah Club to making his mark in London's music scene up until his Monterey Pop triumph, the film presents an intimate portrait of the sensitive young musician on the verge of becoming a rock legend.

entry.title: Verruckt - The First Launch

media:group.media:description:
Filmed from the GARMIN VIRB Action camera, get a look at the first ride down the Verruckt Waterslide. Featuring waterpark designer Jeff Henry and ride engineer John Schooley -- see the insanity that is responsible for the world's tallest waterslide. www.schlitterbahndg.com
See the raw first drop POV footage: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6o2kGw0GbA0
To clarify - the GoPro's seen in the video belong to the Travel Channel for their footage of XTREME Waterparks. Working with Garmin, we are using their action camera for our shots. We are very happy with the technology in these cameras as they provide GPS, Gyro and accelerometer data to assist us with testing.
For inquires contact Nick Tyson at 512-466-1065
